	人生ｵﾜﾀ＼(^o^)／<br>

	<a href="https://github.com/Difegue/LANraragi"> LANraragi [% version %] </a> 
	- <a onclick="openThemeOverlay()" style="cursor:pointer">Change Theme</a>
